               "text": "Part of: Apple Watch Stay Connected with Us! Follow TechnoBuffalo The Apple Watch has arrived, and to mark the occasion, we are giving one away. We’re already giving away an Apple Watch Sport that we used in our review. But because everyone has a different style, the winner of this giveaway (thanks to our friends at StackSocial) will get to pick the model and strap of their choice up to a value of $750. Apple offers the Watch in two sizes of display and three finishes, with six different straps in a range of colors, so it is only fair that you get to choose your ideal combination. Whether that is a Sport edition with a lime green fluoroelastomer band, or the standard edition with a Milanese loop, is entirely up to you. To enter for your chance to win this technologically advanced timepiece, visit the link below, and hit the big green button to create an account and claim your entry. Then, share your entry on social media for more chances to win. ",
